text: Shigeo Homma (19 April 1904 - 3 November 1974) was a Japanese gymnast. He competed in three events at the 1932 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1904 births Category:1974 deaths Category:Japanese male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Japan Category:Gymnasts at the 1932 Summer Olympics Category:Place of birth missing
